heading: Maddux Watch Dungeon Guide
content: Maddux Watch slow dungeon with the low value . This dungeon is best for its Renown rewards, so complete it if you need the extra Scosglen points, but don't run it over and over again for leveling. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
